<div id="review_2750193040" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2750193040" />
    <a title="Kevin Shepherd" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/67532575-kevin-shepherd"><img alt="Kevin Shepherd" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623927409p2/67532575.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2750193040?book_show_action=true">Mar 04, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kevin Shepherd" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kevin Shepherd" href="/user/show/67532575-kevin-shepherd">Kevin Shepherd</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140189377" href="/book/show/149877.Seize_the_Day">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin-shepherd?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin-shepherd?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin-shepherd?shelf=short-reads">short-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin-shepherd?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin-shepherd?shelf=own">own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2750193040" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1920991337113785241">With the exception of maybe Franz Kafka, Saul Bellow writes chaotic despair better than anyone I know. ‘Seize the Day’ is the ironically titled chronicle of an existence that is going completely to shit. Bellow crafts a phantom of hope, and then he shreds it - and then he shreds the shreds. I enjoyed this immensely but empathy forbids me from ever reading it again.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


