<span id="freeTextContainer12029752850179978007">I cannot sum up the book better than the one line of the GR book description:<br/><br/>&quot;<u>Deftly interweaving humor and pathos</u>, Saul Bellow evokes in the climactic events of one day the full drama of one (middle-aged) man&apos;s search to affirm his own worth and humanity.&quot;<br/><br/>I have underlined what should be stressed and added in parenthesis what is lacking.<br/><br/>Addendum:<br/>*Jewish NY humor at its best.<br/>*Bellow captures with pathos how it feels to be middle-aged.<br/>*<i>Carpe diem</i> is for some beyond one&apos;s fingertips. <br/><br/>Grover Gardne</span>
  <span id="freeText12029752850179978007" style="display:none">I cannot sum up the book better than the one line of the GR book description:<br /><br />"<u>Deftly interweaving humor and pathos</u>, Saul Bellow evokes in the climactic events of one day the full drama of one (middle-aged) man's search to affirm his own worth and humanity."<br /><br />I have underlined what should be stressed and added in parenthesis what is lacking.<br /><br />Addendum:<br />*Jewish NY humor at its best.<br />*Bellow captures with pathos how it feels to be middle-aged.<br />*<i>Carpe diem</i> is for some beyond one's fingertips. <br /><br />Grover Gardner’s reading of the audiobook is beyond reproach. Five stars for the narration.<br /><br /><br />******************<br /><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6551.Herzog" title="Herzog by Saul Bellow" rel="nofollow noopener">Herzog</a> 4 stars<br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11907.The_Victim" title="The Victim by Saul Bellow" rel="nofollow noopener">The Victim</a> 4 stars<br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/52782.Seize_the_Day" title="Seize the Day by Saul Bellow" rel="nofollow noopener">Seize the Day</a> 3 stars<br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9873.Dangling_Man" title="Dangling Man by Saul Bellow" rel="nofollow noopener">Dangling Man</a> 3 stars<br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11908.The_Adventures_of_Augie_March" title="The Adventures of Augie March by Saul Bellow" rel="nofollow noopener">The Adventures of Augie March</a> 2 stars<br /></span>
