<span id="freeTextContainer17032404514345136386">Warning: This gem of a novella packs a punch. It is the story of a middle-aged man on his day of reckoning. Although it lacked the humor promised on the back cover, the pathos more than makes up for it. I&apos;d better call Saul. I want to ask him about the title. </span>
  <span id="freeText17032404514345136386" style="display:none">Warning: This gem of a novella packs a punch. It is the story of a middle-aged man on his day of reckoning. Although it lacked the humor promised on the back cover, the pathos more than makes up for it. I'd better call Saul. I want to ask him about the title. </span>
